    "en": "Assess the symptoms of diabetes such as distress, disabilities, depression, anxiety, disordered eating, visual and hearing impairments, cognitive capacities, and other geriatric syndromes using a Comprehensive Geriatric Assessment at the initial visit, at periodic intervals, and when there is a change in disease, treatment, or life circumstance; including caregivers and family members in this assessment.",
